razer (1.0-0ubuntu1) trusty; urgency=low

  * Initial release of the driver, daemon and Python library.
  * Support added:
      * Keyboards
        * Blackwidow Classic
        * Ultimate 2012
        * Ultimate 2013
        * Ultimate 2016
        * Chroma (TE/X)
        * Blade Stealth
      * Mice
        * Mamba Chroma (Wireless only)
        * Abyssus
      * Peripherals
        * Firefly
        * Tartarus
  * Autostart at login.

